reviews.review_text:
Better Sounding UpGrade Charlie has done it again.  This is big improvement from earlier circulating sound boards.  Gone is the drop out at the ending o West LA Fadeaway.  Definitely a 4 star sound quality.  

This made fine background music on my computer instead of watching the same old crap on TV...
4-26-83 Nice performance and very good sound quality from C Miller.

There's no place like home..There's no place like home I always go back to this show for a listen..Love the SHAKEDOWN!! The sound quality is on point and a well played show..in the 2nd set I"m always down for a Help>Slip>Franklins..and a sweet Dew..so GIVE IT A WHIRL

grate stuff yeah,  good  show,  good  sound,  good  dance vibe
shake your thang to this,  while you still can

I just can't.. Songs are too sped up. Jerry 's voice is so craggy between 82 and 85 it just pains me to hear it. If you think this is good, more power to you. I will stick with my favorite years, 72',77',89' and 90'.
